c: 33
v: 13
t: "Kaadu nabiyow cus, munaafiqhiin butta, Yasrib maraw (Madiinah mara kinnuk) a-aracal madabah litoonum mantoonuuy qeebih duudda mantoonuk, toysa sinni buxaaxih gaca iyyen waqdi moominiinik, keenik hortá gacimih Nabiik idini esserak, diggah ni- buxaaxi dibuk raqteeh, qaduwwik reebu mali iyyan. Is dibuk maraaqinnay usun qeebik kudimik- sa faxaanam malon"